ch die Darstellung des Distributionsmediums mit der zunehmenden Verbreitung von Clips im Internet wandelt.  aThe music video as a place of media reflection - a media-cultural study on the depiction of television in audiovisual clips.  afunded by Geschwister Boehringer-Stiftung Ingelheim am Rhein  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDiscourse. 0aDiskurs. 0aFernsehen. 0aMedia Aesthetics. 0aMedia Studies. 0aMedia. 0aMedien. 0aMedienwissenschaft. 0aMedienästhetik. 0aMusic Video. 0aPopkultur. 0aPopular culture. 0aReflexion. 0aTelevision. 0aVideo. 0aVideoclip. 4aDiskurs. 4aFernsehen. 4aMedien. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aMedienästhetik. 4aPopkultur. 4aReflexion. 4aVideo. 4aVideoclip. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aDiscourse.  aMedia Aesthetics.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aPopular Culture.  aTelevision.  aVideo.2 aGeschwister Boehringer-Stiftung Ingelheim am Rheinefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839439876zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839439876423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839439876/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018